ab hm basic smjhenge ki server ko create krenge aur usko database se connect kaise krte hai hm wo smjhenge 

server ko initiate krne ke liye hamare pas command hoti hai 
                                                           npm init -y
ab hme ek package install krna hoga jiska nam hai express                                                           
                                                           npm i express

ab hm ek folder create krenge src and iss folder ke andr ek file create krenge app.js                                                           
app.js ke mainly do hi kam hota hai ek server create krna , aur dusra kam hota hai server config krna 